extendedInfo.description: This is just a new app im testing out from a cool new service i came across on the Google machine. The website is called http://www.appsgeyser.com and basically it lets you turn any website into an app. And best of all its free. So go check it out and make an app or two. They even have their own gallery of apps made by other people who have used the service. Its pretty nifty keen lol.
